creator: Integrated Technology Group
descriptionHtml: The EduWave™ app gives students access to all the power of the EduWave system on mobile device. Students will have access to their grades, books, courses, assessments, assignments and much more. The EduWave app not only helps users become more efficient, effective and productive but also improves student learning and engagement.
descriptionShort: Android client for EduWave, the comprehensive elearning platform

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
General Features:
- New attractive look and feel for the whole app.
- Enhanced application user experience.

For Students:
- Navigate through course content easily.
- Enjoy full access to all Multimedia library content.
- Submit your answers on a vote.

For Teachers:
- Upload course content easily
- Enjoy full access to all Multimedia library content

Bugs fixes
